OTC/Ito-san,
Thank you for your continued support.

Regarding the Livelink logs from Mitsubishi Chemical Engineering,
we are currently unable to identify the cause,
so we will organize the information and work to isolate the problem, including environmental factors.
To that end, we would like to confirm whether there were any issues with [Service for UNIX].


There are various possible causes for the process downtime,
and in addition to audit function load issues and CA issues,
for the purpose of isolating the cause, could you please report
the details that led to the process downtime?

Note: Regarding the [Service for UNIX] issue, this may not be directly related to the Livelink environment,
but we are informing you of it.

http://www.microsoft.com/japan/support/kb/articles/JP294/3/80.htm
http://www.microsoft.com/JAPAN/support/kb/articles/JP283/0/13.HTM?LN=JA&SD=S
O&FR=0

We hope to resolve the process downtime as soon as possible
and appreciate your cooperation.

Canon Sales Co., Ltd.
Masayoshi Ito

